      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has significant mechanical issues that require attention and may not be reliable for everyday use. The exterior shows substantial wear, including scratches, dents, and faded paint. The interior is also worn with visible damage to upholstery and trim. Best suited for someone looking for a project car or parts.",
